Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大总统回来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像他在正门破坏了布里克斯的战车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里克斯的山猴子们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集合剩下的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺回作战本部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大总统在正门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是第一次见到本人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扯断我孙女手臂的人 是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}永远的休假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牺牲一般人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些高官获得长生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,统一世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德雷大总统也是明白真相还在继续的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是为了这个目的而生的国家领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好犹豫的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了制造没有战争的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了那个就要毁灭一次吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:02:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是毁灭 是再生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们炼金术师说的再构筑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带给一般国民的不是死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在我们的体内获取永生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一起统一世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一是全
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们亚美斯多利斯被选中的人 将成为一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们准备怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想独吞好处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么放着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你们跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 就向那位大人说些好话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能遵从长官的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经不知道该相信谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了这个份上还能犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使跟从不能信任的长官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不能说是忠诚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是自我欺瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择不会让自己的灵魂蒙羞的活法就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城里有我家人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准将阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战本部 情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各处的中央兵都活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下现在何处？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大总统办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生存者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和办公室周围的我方人员无法取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里被中央兵包围的可能性很大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们那里有危险就逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍弃我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里又到处是敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央兵整理队形冲进这里也只是时间问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下降到一定程度后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和来的时候一样 挖个逃脱用的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:05:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃脱？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也需要时间调整态势吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然这么想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们能通过气息知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不详的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手臂被取走的旧伤隐隐作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀哦呀 没想到会有观众来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是制造了金格·布拉德雷的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作了大总统…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说 你是那边的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为你在广播局 没想到专程亲自来访
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省了我不少事真谢谢你 马斯坦古君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们稍微陪他们玩会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:07:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人偶兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 和那个动作明显不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是可能会成为金格·布拉德雷的男人们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出生后立刻被集中起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是为了这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在专门的教育和训练中成长的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 第12次实验
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金格·布拉德雷诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这些人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 他们一直积累着战斗经验
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然比不上金格·布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 该死的叛乱军
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔掉反而会失血过多而死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很危险的 大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并非故意…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然这种武器感觉很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明比我年纪还大 动作倒是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爷 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清国的皇子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子 麟…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别擅自出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前切断手臂的女孩一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又这样为了无法舍弃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让自己的生命处于危险的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快快扔了我这种无法战斗的老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我变得和那个男人一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王是为了人民而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人民就不存在王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要舍弃自己国家的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我所追求的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不适合做王的男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可必须要打倒才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了 休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休假…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要一次休假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:11:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快硬化 古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护少主的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主 成为王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这老头子 要在这里永远地休假了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起去地狱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌上这条命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没法伤他一毫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真没脸见您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使有着神一般的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从看不见的地方来的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是没有办法躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通向地狱的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我陪你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 万分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会掉水沟 一会撞路灯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你驾驶水平真差 小胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦 用那破车能到这里就谢天谢地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到这里了 还吵什么架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 快点找到进入地下的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是马斯坦古大佐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行得顺利就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超出常人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也该有个限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你背后全空了 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有放心交付的部下 所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理之门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术的禁忌人体炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝试它的术师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是打开过真理之门的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然要支付相应的通行费
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:16:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔利克兄弟牺牲了自己身体的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面被拿走了一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 做到这个程度所明白的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是人体炼成 不会成功而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 这种话题军人没兴趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开过真理之门的人就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们所说的人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定能成为了解敌人企图的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜打开真理之门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜牺牲自己的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想再次见面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你们心里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论花多少代价
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:17:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想再见一次的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是和军人无缘的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对死人的依恋没有任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有为了不让他们死而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威胁他说出所知道的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那青梅竹马被当成了人质的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他却一点都没有透露
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是说了一句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请理解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那眼神和我们军人的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及被称为军队走狗的炼金术师的眼神不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不能再失去什么重要东西的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不听劝告的小孩子的眼神？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说没有被那直白的眼神打动的话 那是谎话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那可以说是愚昧的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果能在这场战斗中杀开活路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 差不多该开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,16号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,17号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,21号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,23号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,26号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 这只是第一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这中央都市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有几个大总统直辖的炼金术研究所吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在所使用的是市内4处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五研究所？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5个顶点的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼成阵？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 那个弧形的地下道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画着连接研究所的圆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 亨克尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这里刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用这墙壁挖个逃脱用的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离我远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就在这里分别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还不得不留在这里战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下面恐怕是敌人的中枢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放过奇袭的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 伊兹米·卡迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才该谢谢您 阿姆斯壮少将
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯君？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:21:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.23,0:22:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢 钢…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,愤怒产于悲伤之绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.98,0:24:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,两个灵魂寄宿于同一个身体
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.34,0:24:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,开始歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.33,0:24:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.06,0:24:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.89,0:24:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第58话 人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.87,0:24:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使死去也要继续保护
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.22,0:24:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是本愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:07.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}终于找到了  全新的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:11.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}日月却来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:16.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}我前往的地方  不是“未来”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:20.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}仅仅不停地追赶着“过去”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:26.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}不停地鸣响着 那过去的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:31.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}仿佛无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:36.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}差不多了吧  那厌倦搜索的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:41.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}丢掉心里的纠结
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:46.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  总有会停的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:52.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这么漫长  却如此冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:57.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  为什么会选择我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:02.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}笼罩着我  真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:06.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  已经忘了停
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:12.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天依然持续下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:17.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在默默撑开的雨伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:28.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}接近那温暖的怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:41.84,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}从那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:46.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}就决定不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:51.65,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}即使承担再多的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.65,0:22:56.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仍有无法原谅的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:00.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经无法回到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:02.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:07.79,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还没有做成任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.79,0:23:13.04,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的记忆之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:18.92,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}又有一块  消逝而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:21.93,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回望今日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.93,0:23:24.68,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:29.81,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}期望这个声音总有一天可以传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.81,0:23:32.19,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.19,0:23:34.90,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在风停止的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:39.61,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仰望天空追寻着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.36,0:23:46.94,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}在黎明前散发的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:52.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}将会变成彩虹
